label.value: Concentration After the Nth Dose

value.value: The concentration at the Nth dose.

label.value: Concentration After the Nth Dose by Body Mass Index

value.value: The concentration at the Nth dose divided by the body mass index.

label.value: Recurrent Rectal Carcinoma

value.value: The reemergence of rectal carcinoma after a period of remission.

label.value: Concentration After the Nth Dose by Dose

value.value: The concentration at the Nth dose divided by the dose.

label.value: Concentration After the Nth Dose by Surface Area

value.value: The concentration at the Nth dose divided by the surface area.

label.value: Concentration After the Nth Dose by Weight

value.value: The concentration at the Nth dose divided by the weight.

label.value: Initial Concentration Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: Initial concentration divided by the body mass index. Given only for bolus IV models.

label.value: Initial Concentration Normalized by Dose

value.value: Initial concentration divided by the dose. Given only for bolus IV models.

label.value: Initial Concentration Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: Initial concentration divided by the surface area. Given only for bolus IV models.

label.value: Initial Concentration Normalized by Weight

value.value: Initial concentration divided by the weight. Given only for bolus IV models.

label.value: Last Concentration Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The concentration corresponding to Tlast divided by the body mass index.

label.value: Last Concentration Normalized by Dose

value.value: The concentration corresponding to Tlast divided by the dose.

label.value: Last Concentration Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The concentration corresponding to Tlast divided by the surface area.

label.value: Localized Malignant Mesothelioma

value.value: A malignant mesothelioma with the gross appearance of a circumscribed serosal lesion and the microscopic appearance of diffuse malignant mesothelioma, without evidence of diffuse spread.

label.value: Last Concentration Normalized by Weight

value.value: The concentration corresponding to Tlast divided by the weight.

label.value: Last Measurable Excretion Rate Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The last measurable (positive) excretion rate divided by the body mass index.

label.value: Last Measurable Excretion Rate Normalized by Dose

value.value: The last measurable (positive) excretion rate divided by the dose.

label.value: Last Measurable Excretion Rate Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The last measurable (positive) excretion rate divided by the surface area.

label.value: Last Measurable Excretion Rate Normalized by Weight

value.value: The last measurable (positive) excretion rate divided by the weight.

label.value: Maximum Observed Excretion Rate Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The maximum observed excretion rate divided by the body mass index.

label.value: Maximum Observed Excretion Rate Normalized by Dose

value.value: The maximum observed excretion rate divided by the dose.

label.value: Maximum Observed Excretion Rate Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The maximum observed excretion rate divided by the surface area.

label.value: Maximum Observed Excretion Rate Normalized by Weight

value.value: The maximum observed excretion rate divided by the weight.

label.value: Total Clearance Observed by Fraction Dose Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The observed total body clearance for extravascular administration based on the fraction of dose absorbed and divided by the body mass index.

label.value: Valinomycin

value.value: A cyclic depsipeptide isolated from the bacterium Streptomyces fulvissimus.  As a potassium-specific ionophore, mould element causes loss of mitochondrial membrane potential, thereby initiating cellular apoptosis. (NCI04)

label.value: Recurrent Nasopharyngeal Carcinoma

value.value: The reemergence of nasopharyngeal carcinoma after a period of remission.

label.value: Total Clearance Observed by Fraction Dose Normalized by Dose

value.value: The observed total body clearance for extravascular administration based on the fraction of dose absorbed and divided by the dose.

label.value: Total Clearance Observed by Fraction Dose Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The observed total body clearance for extravascular administration based on the fraction of dose absorbed and divided by the surface area.

label.value: Total Clearance Observed by Fraction Dose Normalized by Weight

value.value: The observed total body clearance for extravascular administration based on the fraction of dose absorbed and divided by the weight.

label.value: Total Clearance Observed Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The observed total body clearance for intravascular administration divided by the body mass index.

label.value: Total Clearance Observed Normalized by Dose

value.value: The observed total body clearance for intravascular administration divided by the dose.

label.value: Total Clearance Observed Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The observed total body clearance for intravascular administration divided by the surface area.

label.value: Total Clearance Observed Normalized by Weight

value.value: The observed total body clearance for intravascular administration divided by the weight.

label.value: Volume of Distribution Observed Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The observed volume of distribution associated with the terminal slope following intravascular administration divided by the body mass index.

label.value: Volume of Distribution Observed Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The observed volume of distribution associated with the terminal slope following intravascular administration divided by the surface area.

label.value: Volume of Distribution Observed Normalized by Weight

value.value: The observed volume of distribution associated with the terminal slope following intravascular administration divided by the weight.

label.value: Recurrent Hypopharyngeal Carcinoma

value.value: The reemergence of hypopharyngeal carcinoma after a period of remission.

label.value: Volume of Distribution of Fraction Dose Observed Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The observed volume of distribution of the absorbed fraction associated with the terminal slope following extravascular administration, where F equals the fraction of dose absorbed, divided by the body mass index.

label.value: Volume of Distribution of Fraction Dose Observed Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The observed volume of distribution of the absorbed fraction associated with the terminal slope following extravascular administration, where F equals the fraction of dose absorbed, divided by the surface area.

label.value: Volume of Distribution of Fraction Dose Observed Normalized by Weight

value.value: The observed volume of distribution of the absorbed fraction associated with the terminal slope following extravascular administration, where F equals the fraction of dose absorbed, divided by the weight.

label.value: Percent Recovered Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The percentage of the dose that is recovered from the specimen type, from dosing to end of the current collection interval divided by the body mass index.

label.value: Percent Recovered Normalized by Dose

value.value: The percentage of the dose that is recovered from the specimen type, from dosing to end of the current collection interval divided by the dose.

label.value: Percent Recovered Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The percentage of the dose that is recovered from the specimen type, from dosing to end of the current collection interval divided by the surface area.

label.value: Percent Recovered Normalized by Weight

value.value: The percentage of the dose that is recovered from the specimen type, from dosing to end of the current collection interval divided by the weight.

label.value: Total Clearance Predicted by Fraction Dose Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The predicted total body clearance for extravascular administration based on the fraction of dose absorbed and divided by the body mass index.

label.value: Total Clearance Predicted by Fraction Dose Normalized by Dose

value.value: The predicted total body clearance for extravascular administration based on the fraction of dose absorbed and divided by the dose.

label.value: Total Clearance Predicted by Fraction Dose Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The predicted total body clearance for extravascular administration based on the fraction of dose absorbed and divided by the surface area.

label.value: Malignant Colon Neoplasm

value.value: A primary or metastatic malignant neoplasm that affects the colon.  Representative examples include carcinoma, lymphoma, and sarcoma.

label.value: Total Clearance Predicted by Fraction Dose Normalized by Weight

value.value: The predicted total body clearance for extravascular administration based on the fraction of dose absorbed and divided by the weight.

label.value: Total Clearance Predicted Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The predicted total body clearance for intravascular administration divided by the body mass index.
